message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you for $14,000. I believe it offers significant value at this price point, considering its worth to someone in your position.
Thanks for the offer, Alice. I'm interested, but $14,000 is a bit steep for me. Could you do $11,000?
Thanks for the offer, Bob. I understand your perspective, but $11,000 is quite a bit below its value. Could you meet me halfway at $12,500?
